room_title: Escape room "Pandemic" by Clue'd In Escape Rooms in Columbus
room_description: As a medical investigator, you’re no stranger to exploring unusual activities. When you are informed of the increased consumption of volatile chemicals at a local medical facility, you realize the situation might be more dangerous than it appears. Now you and a team of investigators will have only 60 minutes to discover the lab’s true purpose and hopefully, stop the next PANDEMIC!
